Question: Is the brown car on the right?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n480253.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='car')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the car?')
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'brown' else 'no'")
ANSWER2=VQA(image=IMAGE,question='What is on the right side of the image?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER1} == {ANSWER2} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
